summary:
Smart Digital Business Network - The business model of the Smart Digital Business Network is a combination of a fully automated sales system and the SunMoney Community Power Plant program.

 SDBN1 - The SDBN1 token was initially launched on the Unit Network on May 1, 2022.

 SDBN2 - The SDBN2 token was launched on the BSC blockchain on November 1, 2022.
